ch.iserver.ace.net.core
Interface RemoteDocumentProxyExt

All Superinterfaces:
RemoteDocumentProxy
All Known Implementing Classes:
RemoteDocumentProxyImpl
public interface RemoteDocumentProxyExt
extends RemoteDocumentProxy

Interface extension of RemoteDocumentProxy for the network layer. It adds methods concerning the join and invitation process of other users.
